the author icq "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==============================================================

NAME
----

the author icq - Displays the ICQ number for the author of a post. Prior to [WordPress

SYNOPSIS
--------

Displays the ICQ number for the author of a post. Prior to [WordPress
2.0](/Version_2.0 "Version 2.0"), the **ICQ** field was set in the
user's profile, but the field is currently not accessible in the
[Administration](/Administration_Panels "Administration Panels") \>
[Profile](/Administration_Panels#Your_Profile "Administration Panels")
\> [Your Profile](/Your_Profile_SubPanel "Your Profile SubPanel") panel.
This tag must be used within [The Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop").

REPLACE WITH
------------

No replacement exists for this template tag, as the field was removed
from the [Profile
panel](/Your_Profile_SubPanel "Your Profile SubPanel").

USAGE
-----

`  <?php the_author_icq(); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

This tag does not accept any parameters.

EXAMPLE
-------

    <p>Contact me on ICQ: <?php the_author_icq(); ?></p>

CHANGE LOG
----------

-   Since: 0.71
-   Deprecated: ?
-   Replace By: none

